{"tid":1729062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（自煮燃發？）上水警署起火","createTime":"2019-11-17T06:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T07:14:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"07550e049fbc32ad0469165a26c2a03cd28983e3","tid":1729062,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:06:05.000Z","msg":"上水警署遭縱火。凌晨4時48分，警方懷疑有人向上水警署投擲汽油彈，導致外牆及泊車處有被燒痕迹，現場留有懷疑汽油彈碎片。警員將碎片檢走作進一步檢驗，案件列作縱火處理，交由大埔警區刑事調查隊第八隊跟進，暫時未有人被捕。事件中無人受傷。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191117/s00001/1573960260152/上水警署遭縱火-警疑有人擲汽油彈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191117%2Fs00001%2F1573960260152%2F%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E9%81%AD%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB-%E8%AD%A6%E7%96%91%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88&d=%2BzDF6%2Fqe%2FxCukoiAfbFcJ4WZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=4c8897b1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20191117%2Fs00001%2F1573960260152%2F%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E8%AD%A6%E7%BD%B2%E9%81%AD%E7%B8%B1%E7%81%AB-%E8%AD%A6%E7%96%91%E6%9C%89%E4%BA%BA%E6%93%B2%E6%B1%BD%E6%B2%B9%E5%BD%88&h=21f01728\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20191117/s00001/1573960260152/上水警署遭縱火-警疑有人擲汽油彈</a>"},{"pid":"4293957967f8b60e1a5dc30ed0e8865669cf34ea","tid":1729062,"uid":73826,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"唔想睇片"},{"pid":"f5e9e03eaba332fffd64821db6d88da6d541b272","tid":1729062,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:21:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">開佢老味花，營救手足啊屌！！！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"9db51c5bf66c08b4a497fef2e94d7a73c5f714e8","tid":1729062,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T06:22:28.000Z","msg":"燒唔燒到到啲車先"},{"pid":